"struct:24996a959edda5b1b1e8de6e553c270f"
"struct"
"batchingTx"
"batchingTx"
"pkg/dalgo2ghingitdb/batching.go"
"go"
117
124
5
1
"batchingTx implements dal.ReadwriteTransaction by buffering all writes.\n\nSingleRecord collections: each Set / Insert encodes the new record\ncontent and stores a TreeChange in bufferedFiles; Delete stores a\nTreeChange with nil Content (deletion).\n\nMapOfRecords collections: the in-flight state of each map file lives in\nworkingMaps. On first touch we read the current remote state via\nensureMapLoaded; subsequent Set / Insert / Delete modify the in-memory\nmap. At flush time, every modified working map is re-encoded into one\nTreeChange."
""
